{"tid":2096928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國安法授權警察限制受調查的人離開香港","createTime":"2020-07-06T12:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T12:52:30.000Z","uid":304281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1df50d3dde1d31424849e81fbac19865d0fdd516","tid":2096928,"uid":304281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"「國安法」第四十三條實施細則刊憲，規定警務處國安部執法時可採取措施：<br />\n1.　為搜證而搜查有關地方 2.　限制受調查的人離開香港 3.　凍結、限制、沒收及充公與危害國家安全罪行相關財產 4.　移除危害國家安全的信息及要求協助 5. 向外國及台灣政治性組織及其代理人要求就涉港活動提供資料 6. 進行截取通訊及秘密監察的授權申請 7. 提供資料和提交物料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=29609&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fott-news.i-cable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D29609%26ct%3D1&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FtArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=d503fab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=29609&amp;ct=1</a>"},{"pid":"f1a587c2ee64f220daae99ad97ae6d7f038d7594","tid":2096928,"uid":304281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:41:15.000Z","msg":"而家想走都走唔到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca9e2f162b841359c8de17c125d6eb427d77a41","tid":2096928,"uid":233905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"5.人哋真係唔會理你地班共產黨養嘅死曱甴？<br />\n6.屌你老母你哋不嬲都唔使授權㗎啦"}]}